00:42:16,470 --> 00:42:20,940
Your husband, Qian Cheng, was a senior
executive at Lyuyun Pharmaceuticals.

575
00:42:21,560 --> 00:42:24,070
He hanged himself a year ago.

576
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:27,230
How could you know about my family?

577
00:42:27,230 --> 00:42:31,000
I also know Qian Cheng
didn't kill himself.

578
00:42:32,540 --> 00:42:33,150
Yes.

579
00:42:34,890 --> 00:42:36,270
He didn't.

580
00:42:36,440 --> 00:42:39,600
My husband was
definitely killed by Zhao Qian.

581
00:42:41,840 --> 00:42:45,060
When he lost his mind over her,

582
00:42:45,090 --> 00:42:46,960
I even hired a private detective

583
00:42:46,960 --> 00:42:48,590
to investigate Zhao Qian,

584
00:42:49,280 --> 00:42:50,540
but nothing came of it.

585
00:42:51,410 --> 00:42:52,930
Private detective?

586
00:42:53,960 --> 00:42:55,280
Later, he...

587
00:42:55,670 --> 00:42:56,550
he died.

588
00:42:57,900 --> 00:43:00,800
Even fewer people
would believe what I say.

589
00:43:01,630 --> 00:43:04,490
They all said it was suicide.

590
00:43:07,840 --> 00:43:08,840
Zhao Qian

591
00:43:09,800 --> 00:43:11,320
even sent people to threaten me,

592
00:43:11,320 --> 00:43:12,720
telling me to keep quiet.

593
00:43:13,540 --> 00:43:14,980
For my son's sake, I...

594
00:43:18,590 --> 00:43:19,450
I could only...

595
00:43:20,600 --> 00:43:24,740
Qian Cheng did hang himself,

596
00:43:25,450 --> 00:43:28,380
but the one who
put the rope around his neck

597
00:43:28,600 --> 00:43:29,900
was someone else.

598
00:43:32,470 --> 00:43:34,000
I know.

599
00:43:34,670 --> 00:43:35,920
But I have no evidence.

600
00:43:35,920 --> 00:43:38,320
This is what makes
Zhao Qian so formidable.

601
00:43:38,340 --> 00:43:40,470
She never does the dirty work herself.

602
00:43:40,760 --> 00:43:43,180
Instead, she coerces and controls others.

603
00:43:43,420 --> 00:43:45,260
That's how Qian Cheng died.

604
00:43:55,070 --> 00:43:56,880
It's okay.

605
00:43:56,900 --> 00:43:58,570
Your son's very sensible.

606
00:43:59,220 --> 00:44:02,140
I wish he wasn't.

607
00:44:03,240 --> 00:44:04,470
He's just a child,

608
00:44:05,760 --> 00:44:07,960
and Zhao Qian still went after him.

609
00:44:12,550 --> 00:44:14,710
I wish I could kill her.

610
00:44:16,710 --> 00:44:18,230
If you really mean that,

611
00:44:18,960 --> 00:44:20,190
I can help you.

612
00:44:23,240 --> 00:44:24,640
If Zhao Qian doesn't die,

613
00:44:24,940 --> 00:44:26,650
more people will suffer,

614
00:44:27,190 --> 00:44:28,800
not just you and your son.

615
00:44:32,590 --> 00:44:35,120
I don't... I don't know how to kill her.

616
00:44:35,580 --> 00:44:36,930
You don't have to do it.

617
00:44:38,070 --> 00:44:40,150
Just call Zhao Qian

618
00:44:40,320 --> 00:44:41,380
and ask her to meet.

619
00:44:41,800 --> 00:44:43,190
She won't come.

620
00:44:43,210 --> 00:44:44,080
She will.

621
00:44:44,440 --> 00:44:45,150
Why?

622
00:44:46,760 --> 00:44:48,820
Because she has a guilty conscience.

623
00:44:56,150 --> 00:44:56,390
[Protein]

624
00:44:56,390 --> 00:44:57,170
We've

625
00:44:57,230 --> 00:44:57,930
introduced advanced automation

626
00:44:57,930 --> 00:44:59,320
[Vitamin]

627
00:44:59,320 --> 00:45:00,670
and information systems.

628
00:45:00,670 --> 00:45:01,480
The factory implements

629
00:45:01,480 --> 00:45:04,280
a fully intelligent management process
from raw material procurement

630
00:45:04,280 --> 00:45:05,480
to product delivery.

631
00:45:14,280 --> 00:45:15,440
Now, through the glass,

632
00:45:15,440 --> 00:45:16,110
we can see

633
00:45:16,110 --> 00:45:18,150
products on different production lines

634
00:45:18,150 --> 00:45:19,900
being systematically filled,

635
00:45:20,000 --> 00:45:21,400
sealed, and coded.

636
00:45:30,180 --> 00:45:32,320
[Zhao Qian,
do you want to play Hide and Seek?]

637
00:45:34,620 --> 00:45:35,750
I need to take a call.

638
00:45:39,550 --> 00:45:40,360
Who is this?

639
00:45:40,360 --> 00:45:41,760
I sell beef offal.

640
00:45:42,860 --> 00:45:44,250
I'm Qian Cheng's wife.

641
00:45:44,490 --> 00:45:45,450
Ms. Fang,

642
00:45:46,280 --> 00:45:47,200
what's the matter?

643
00:45:47,200 --> 00:45:48,890
Today I finally confirmed

644
00:45:50,370 --> 00:45:52,720
it was really you who killed Qian Cheng.

645
00:45:52,800 --> 00:45:53,630
Confirmed?

646
00:45:54,710 --> 00:45:55,640
What do you mean?

647
00:45:55,650 --> 00:45:58,640
Nothing stays hidden forever.

648
00:45:59,800 --> 00:46:01,320
Fortunately, Qian Cheng
left something behind,

649
00:46:01,320 --> 00:46:03,380
otherwise he would have died in vain.

650
00:46:03,880 --> 00:46:05,280
What did he leave behind?

651
00:46:05,740 --> 00:46:06,500
Zhao Qian,

652
00:46:06,980 --> 00:46:08,060
you're finished.

653
00:46:09,880 --> 00:46:11,280
What exactly do you want?

654
00:46:11,330 --> 00:46:12,530
Tonight at 8 o'clock,

655
00:46:12,740 --> 00:46:15,000
I'll be waiting for you at Xinggang Park.

656
00:46:15,150 --> 00:46:16,550
You must come alone.

657
00:46:18,220 --> 00:46:19,560
You'll find out then.

658
00:46:34,350 --> 00:46:40,100
[The Perfect Suspect]
